author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, “No Kings” protests were staged across the country this weekend. The protesters bravely stood up against a monarchy that doesn’t exist in this country. We’ll recap the sad and sometimes disturbing spectacle. Also, Trump announces a renewed effort for mass deportations in major cities across the country. But what about amnesty for illegal aliens who work for farms and hotels? Will that really happen? Plus, war breaks out between Iran and Israel. Will we get involved? Should we? We’ll discuss. And, the media celebrated Father’s Day the same way they always do: by lecturing and scolding fathers.
